        "content": "<p>Is there a way to take an <code>int</code> and a proof that it's nonnegative and cast it into a <code>nat</code>?<br>\nMore specifically, if I have natural numbers <code>n k</code> and a proof of <code>k+1 \\le n</code>, how to prove that <code>n- (k+1)+1 = n-k</code>?</p>",
