    },
    {
        "content": "<p>These seem like two different questions, but: see <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib_docs/tactics.html#lift\">tactic#lift</a> for the first, <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib_docs/tactics.html#omega\">tactic#omega</a> and <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib_docs/tactics.html#zify\">tactic#zify</a> for the second.</p>",
